Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學  茶來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學…長門同學她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:31.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷靜地考慮後就沒說）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（書）（書）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一週後）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（遊戲）（書）（書）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（兩週後）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（遊戲）（遊戲）（書）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（三週後）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（遊戲）（遊戲）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（孤零零…）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（書）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下一天）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（又下一天）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  阿虛  有希有姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多奇怪的衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:29.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（長門Cosplay用服裝）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  難得你在讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這樣才像長門…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！ 這是攻略書！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是長門的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不看這些  解析下遊戲就能攻略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做那種沒意思的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  進行遊戲對戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  來比一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  格鬥遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇角色  還有難易度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難易度？  這是對戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼的難易度呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  作弊啊  作弊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然連長門同學也沒發現我留有備份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉涼子  復活！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪裡失敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長…長門同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經預料到我會復活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（碰巧發現）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  在這裡讓我逃走的話你就完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我完全復活之後定會捲土重…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學…救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那麼  就是要我一起住在這房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  這樣易於監視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（幼兒椅）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…能不能換把椅子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還有別的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如把兩個坐墊疊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上我在用的  坐墊一共只有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那捲起來用就行了  請給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是用椅子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  給你飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  剛被裝在包裡提回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要遭受這種待遇  的確很受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給你換
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是把碗換一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
